text: Yongning Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Pukou District, Nanjing, Jiangsu, China. , it has 8 residential communities and 3 villages under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Jiangsu == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Jiangsu Category:Geography of Nanjing
